                <div>
                  <div class="inquiry"><a href="#">How do I create a new forum post?</a></div>
                </div>
        
                <div class="content">
                 <div class="answers">
                    To create a new forum post, 
                    click on the "Forum" page from the navigation menu.
                    Then, click the "New Post" button. You can choose the 
                    subforum, add a title, and compose your post. Don't forget 
                    to review our posting guidelines before you submit!
                 </div>

                  <div class="comment">
                    <button onclick="Comment()">Comment</button>
                  </div>
