                <!-- * question 2 -->
                <div>
                    <div class="inquiry"><a href="#">Can I edit or delete my forum posts?</a></div>
                  </div>
          
                  <div class="content">
                   <div class="answers">
                    Yes, you can edit or delete your posts. Locate your post,
                     and you'll find options for editing or deleting it. Please note 
                     that there might be time restrictions on editing, and deleted posts
                      may not be recoverable.
                   </div>
  
                    <div class="comment">
                      <button onclick="Comment()">Comment</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                <!-- * question 3 -->
                <div>
                    <div class="inquiry"><a href="#">What are categories and how do I choose the right one for me?</a></div>
                  </div>
          
                  <div class="content">
                   <div class="answers">
                    Subforums are categories within our forum that help organize discussions. When creating a new post,
                    choose the subforum that best matches the topic of your post. If you're unsure,
                     don't worry; our moderators will help categorize it correctly.
                   </div>
  
                    <div class="comment">
                      <button onclick="Comment()">Comment</button>
                    </div>
