                    <div class="inquiry"><a href="#">How do I report inappropriate content or a user's post?</a></div>
                  </div>
          
                  <div class="content">
                   <div class="answers">
                    If you come across inappropriate content or witness behavior that violates our community guidelines,
                    you may message the moderator of the category so it can be handled accordingly.
                   </div>
  
